<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Forgot Password - Project Peak</title>
    <style>
        /* Add your custom CSS styles here */
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .logo {
            max-width: 150px;
            height: auto;
        }

        .content {
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
        }

        .reset-link {
            color: black; /* Link color */
            text-decoration: none; /* Remove underline */
            transition: color 0.3s ease; /* Smooth transition on hover */
            padding: 5px;
            border-radius: 15px;
        }

        .reset-link:hover {
            background-color: lightblue; /* Change color to light blue on hover */
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <img class="logo" src="https://i.imgur.com/KyPxlAG.png" alt="Project Peak Logo">
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <h2>Password Reset Request for Project Peak</h2>
            <p>Dear <%= recipientName %>,</p>
            <p>We received a request to reset the password for your Project Peak account. To proceed with resetting your password, please click the link below:</p>
            <p>
                <a class="reset-link" href="<%= resetLink %>">Reset Password</a>
            </p>
            <p>For security purposes, this link will expire in 1 day. If the link has expired, please request a new password reset.</p>
            <p>If you did not request this password reset, or if you need further assistance, please contact our support team at <%= supportContact %>.</p>
            <p>Thank you for choosing Project Peak. We are always here to assist you.</p>
            <p>Best regards,</p>
            <p><%= senderName %><br><%= senderPosition %><br>Project Peak</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
